Package: gpr
Title: Power Analysis for R
Version: 0.1.0
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R: 
    person("Steve", "Jean-Baptiste", , "stevejb.dev@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive power analysis package implementing statistical 
    power analyses for t-tests, F-tests, chi-square tests, z-tests, and exact 
    tests. Provides five analysis modes (a priori, post hoc, sensitivity, 
    criterion, and compromise), effect size converters, publication-quality 
    plots, an interactive Shiny GUI, and a console menu interface. Methods 
    based on Faul et al. (2007) <doi; 10.3758/BF03193146>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    shiny
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rstudioapi,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/Stevejb1/gpr
BugReports: https://github.com/Stevejb1/gpr/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
